name: LunchTime
0:
”Alexa, ask lunch time lets go for lunch near Seattle”
”Alexa, ask lunch time to search for Indian restaurants in Chicago within ten miles”
”Alexa, launch lunch time and give me a Italian restaurant in Boston”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lunch time
des:
Have you had this situation when you waste time searching for a place to go for lunch?
No worries, lunch time is here, just ask for what cuisine you want to go for, which city or address you are going for lunch and radius from that city.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
